_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0005.tlg001.perseus-grc1:24:118\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Theoc.\">Theoc.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">24.118</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; of troops, <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ὄχθαις Ἴστρου ἐ</foreign>. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0015.tlg001:2:9:1\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Hdn.\">Hdn.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">2.9.1</biblScope></bibl>. </sense><sense n=\"3\" id=\"n39661.3\" level=\"3\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\">. of islands, <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">νῆσοι ἐπὶ Λήμνῳ </foreign>(<foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">-ου</foreign> codd.) <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἐπικείμεναι</foreign> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">lying off</tr_> Lemnos, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0016.tlg001.perseus-grc1:7:6\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Hdt.\">Hdt.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">7.6</biblScope> </bibl>; so <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἐ. τῇ Θρηΐκῃ</foreign> ib.<bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0016.tlg001.perseus-grc1:185\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">185</biblScope> </bibl>; <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἐπὶ [τῇ Λακαίνῃ χώρῃ]</foreign> ib.<bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0016.tlg001.perseus-grc1:235\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">235</biblScope></bibl>, cf. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0003.tlg001.perseus-grc1:4:53\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Th.\">Th.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">4.53</biblScope> </bibl>: abs., <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">αἱ νῆσοι αἱ ἐπικείμεναι</foreign> the islands <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">off the coast</tr_>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLi